text: "In My Cabana" is a song by Polish singer Margaret. It was written by Anderz Wrethov, Linnea Deb, Arash Labaf, and Robert Uhlmann. The song was released for digital download on 10 February 2018 by Extensive Music and Warner Music in various countries, and by Magic Records in Poland. Margaret participated in Melodifestivalen 2018, Sweden's national selection for Eurovision Song Contest 2018, with "In My Cabana". She qualified for the final via Andra chansen ("Second chance" round), and finished in seventh place with 103 points.
